{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_170","type":"agent_message","text":"The pool-manager failure is a broad bean-introspection case, so I’m widening that one type to public methods instead of adding string getters one by one. The registry failure now looks increasingly like native-image classloader semantics rather than a missing registration, but I’m finishing the remaining metadata gaps first so I can confirm that cleanly."}}
